      <p style="color:#8B96A8;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.7;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">Tow It started because the UK vehicle transport industry was (and largely still is) stuck in 2003. Phone calls, fax machines, bidding sites with hidden fees, and no tech at all. We decided to fix it.</p>
    </div>
